text:
Photo: Thearon W. Henderson, Getty Images Francis Owusu wasn’t able to watch the ball into his hands, but he still made one of the year’s best catches. Francis Owusu wasn’t able to watch the ball into his hands, but...
An ESPN crew was there when Francis Owusu was being interviewed by reporters Tuesday. He was on camera earlier when getting a haircut.
